# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# LangGraph Blog Generator — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. Copy this file and rename it to ".env"  (remove the .example)
# 2. Add your API key below (you only need ONE of these)
# 3. Save the file — that's it!
#
# PRIORITY ORDER (first key found wins):
#   1. GROQ_API_KEY      ← RECOMMENDED: 100% free, no credit card needed
#   2. OPENAI_API_KEY    ← requires paid credits
#   3. ANTHROPIC_API_KEY ← requires paid credits
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Option 1: Groq API Key ← BEST FOR DEMOS (Truly Free)
# Model used: llama-3.3-70b-versatile
# Why: Groq runs LLaMA 3 on custom hardware — blazing fast + 100% free tier
# Get key at: https://console.groq.com/keys (sign up, no credit card)
GROQ_API_KEY=

# Option 2: OpenAI API Key (requires paid credits)
# Model used: gpt-4o-mini
OPENAI_API_KEY=

# Option 3: Anthropic API Key (requires paid credits)
# Model used: claude-3-haiku-20240307
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
